What is Angular Material ?
	Reference implementation of Google's Material Design Specification.
References and Links
	https://material.io/guidelines/
	https://material.angular.io/
	https://github.com/angular/material2
	https://github.com/ajtowf/angularmaterial
Material Design
	Why beautiy important ?
		Attractive things work better
	Material is the metaphor
	Bold,graphic and intentional
	Motion provides meaning
Setting up Enviornment
	nodejs,npm,typescript
	visual studio code
	npm i -g @angular/cli	
installing Angular material
	install angular material and angular cdk
	angular cdk(angular component development kit)
	npm i --save @angular/material @angular/cdk
	npm i --save @angular/animations
	import BrowserAnimationModule
	import {BrowserAnimationsModule} from '@angular/platform-browser/animations';
	import {MatButtonModule, MatCheckboxModule} from '@angular/material';
ng g m material --dry-run
ng g m shared/material --flat
Include a theme
npm i --save hammerjs (for gestures support)
import hammer js in main.ts file
Add material icons index.html page
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons"
      rel="stylesheet">

